Module com.example.project3
Package com.example.project3

Class Timeslot

java.lang.Object
com.example.project3.Timeslot
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Timeslot>
public class Timeslot extends Object implements Comparable<Timeslot>
The Timeslot class represents a time slot in a scheduling system, allowing for the creation of time slots corresponding to specific hours and minutes in a 12-slot format, spanning from 9:00 AM to 4:30 PM. The class implements Comparable to allow sorting of timeslots based on their time.
